春田屬[[濕潤性大陸氣候|濕潤性大陸氣候]]（柯本氣候分類法：Dfa），它位於[[龙卷风走廊|龙卷风走廊]]，偶爾會出現較強烈的龍捲風，2005年2月獲聯邦政府資助，以改善其龍捲風警報系統，新系統在2006年11月啟用<ref name=release>[http://www.springfield.il.us/RELEASES/2006%20Releases/NewSirens.htm New City Tornado Sirens are Fully Operational] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928084117/http://www.springfield.il.us/RELEASES/2006%20Releases/NewSirens.htm |date=2007-09-28 }}, Press Release, City of Springfield. Retrieved February 21, 2007.</ref><ref name=lahood>[http://www.house.gov/lahood/20050223Fire.htm Springfield and Quincy Fire Department Awarded $146,646 in Homeland Security Grants] {{Wayback|url=http://www.house.gov/lahood/20050223Fire.htm |date=20070304162058 }}, Press Release, Office of Congressman Ray Lahood, February 23, 2005. Retrieved March 7, 2007.</ref>。

