此地約75%的人口為白人，18%為黑人。<ref>{{cite web|title=Illinois – Race and Hispanic Origin for Selected Cities and Other Places: Earliest Census to 1990 |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau |url=https://www.census.gov/population/www/documentation/twps0076/twps0076.html |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69hd5KAIE?url=http://www.census.gov/population/www/documentation/twps0076/twps0076.html |archivedate=2012-08-06 |df= }}</ref>

==經濟==
該城主要經濟是以政府部門為主。至2002年，該市政府為全市最大僱主，共僱用17,000人。

==教育==

春田現有6所高中，[[南伊利諾大學|南伊利諾大學]]醫學院<ref name=siu>[http://www.siumed.edu/studentaffairs/ Office of Student Affairs] {{Wayback|url=http://www.siumed.edu/studentaffairs/ |date=20070225082657 }}, [[Southern_Illinois_University_School_of_Medicine|Southern Illinois University School of Medicine]]. Retrieved February 24, 2007.</ref>、[[伊利諾大學春田分校|伊利諾大學春田分校]]、[[班尼迪克大学春田分校|班尼迪克大学春田分校]]和[[羅伯特莫里森大學_(伊利諾州)|羅伯特莫里森大學]]位于此地。

